column1: Data collection in progress by Jeremy Pressman (@djpressman, U of Connecticut) and Erica Chenoweth (@EricaChenoweth, U of Denver).
With thanks to Fizza Alam, Camille Chill,and Abbey Vogel for assistance compiling sources.
We are not collecting this data as part of a research project. We are doing this in the public interest. We are not affiliated with any other efforts to collect data on demonstrations.
